    • Field Detail

      • LEGACY_FIELD_NAME

        public static final String LEGACY_FIELD_NAME
        Field name used when storing legacy (lumis.search) fields in big data document. It is used backward compatibility. Data from old index structure that has no corresponding field in a StandardDocument is stored as a field inside this field.
        Since:
        8.1.0
        See Also:
        SearchContentField, Constant Field Values
